Adding Churn Rate KPI 17

Churn Rate



1. Copy and paste the ‘Total Active Customers’ KPI card.
2. Uncheck the ‘Total Active Customers’ and select or drag the ‘Churn Rate’ measure to the Fields section
3. Make the following changes:
General:
Height=114
Width=216
Position =>
Horizontal=1
Vertical=284
Title=On, Text= Churn Rate
Font=Segoe UI (12)
Text color=#FFFFFF
Background color=#094780
Horizontal alignment=Center
Effects =>
Background=On
Background color=#F1F7F6
Transparency=0%
Visual boarder=on
Visual:
Callout Value =>
Font=Segoe UI Semibold (40)
Font color=#F02606
Category label=Off
